                       Block Man 2 DIRECTIONS
                      _______________________


                             OBJECTIVE

   Your objective is to collect all the jewels on a level and then
   exit through the doorway.


                             GAME PLAY

   You can view the level by moving the mouse arrow. Click the left
   mouse button on a spot and Block Man will attempt to walk there.
   Block Man can walk, climb one block heights, and fall any distance.
   Also, you can left click on special objects to use them.


                               HINTS 

   Press the right button to exit a level and return to the menu screen.
   You can then continue the level by pressing the right button from
   the menu screen.


                                MENU

     Click the left mouse button to make the following selections.

          HELP    :   Display the Block Man help.

          SOUND   :   Switch sound between On and Off.

          SPEED   :   Set the animation speed.

          EXIT    :   Exit Block Man 2.

          (#)     :   Click on a numbered ball to play that level.

     Click the right mouse button to continue a level.

                           ***SPECIAL NOTE***
     Hold down the CONTROL key while selecting a level for the solution!

     This Unregistered version of Soleau Software's Block Man 2 contains
     10 levels.



                         *  NOTE WINDOWS USERS  *

     Running Block Man 2 from Windows may cause unexpected results. The
     game should be played by loading it directly from the Dos prompt.



